<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your 2-Factor Authentication Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      color: #111827;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      table-layout: fixed;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0099ff 0%, #00c2ff 100%);
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #0077cc;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background: rgba(240, 246, 255, 0.7);
      border: 1.5px dashed rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.25);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #0077cc;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 0 40px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .security-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.05);
      border-left: 3px solid #dc2626;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: #b91c1c;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>RelayFlow Security</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Two-Factor Authentication Code</h2>
        <p>Hello <strong><%= displayName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>We received a sign-in attempt for your RelayFlow account. To complete the authentication, please enter the security verification code below:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-box">
          <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #4b5563; font-weight: 600;">Verification Code</p>
          <h3 class="otp-code"><%= otp %></h3>
        </div>
        
        <p>This code is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>. If you didn't request this sign-in, please change your password immediately.</p>
        
        <div class="security-note">
          🔒 Never share this security verification code with anyone, including RelayFlow support agents.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> RelayFlow. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Vibrant & Secure Real-Time Messaging Platform.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
